Description: TMJOs Software Center — apps proprietarios TMJOs (Rust)
 Descobre apps proprietarios TMJOs no APT repo via AppStream
 metadata e instala/remove/atualiza via apt + pkexec.
 .
 Reescrito em Rust + gtk4-rs + libadwaita em v2.0.0 (era Python).
 Startup rapido, single binary, zero dependencia Python.
 .
 Features:
   * 3 abas: Apps disponiveis, Instalados, Updates pendentes
   * Detail page com release history + metadata AppStream
   * Install/remove/upgrade async via pkexec + apt-get
   * Visual neon TMJOs (cyan/magenta gradient)
   * Zero tracking, zero promoted apps
